My bridal look🥹🫶🏻

Still remember the first time I saw @houseofmasaba ‘s bridal collection on Instagram and I kinda knew it in my heart that this is it. It was fully my vibe - very fun , fresh and not over the top. Went and tried a few outfits and instantly knew that I wanna be a masaba bride. Got this look fully customised and it was such a smooth process working with them @houseofmasaba @masabagupta 🫶🏻

Missed you the most @mitikakejriwal 🥹

The start of @arhamj98 ‘s solo😂❤️

Some backstory : my husband kept joking he would dance to that super cringey song at our sangeet. You know, the one we saw where the guy was just... too much. I laughed it off, obviously, thinking he’s just teasing me..

Cut to the sangeet. He wasn’t teasing. He was up there ,doing those exact moves. Turns out, my husband’s favorite hobby is embarrassing me, especially on our wedding day. And honestly? I wouldn’t have it any other way😅❤️
